-------------------------------------------------
- V. Grichine changed log to std::log in G4HadronNucleonXsc.cc and
    G4GlauberGribovCrossSection.cc
- D. Wright added log(0) protection in G4NeutronInelasticCrossSection.cc
    and G4ProtonInelasticCrossSection.cc

